==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Brickkiln
<hw>Brick"kiln`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kiln, or
furnace, in which bricks are baked or burnt; or a pile of green bricks,
laid loose, with arches underneath to receive the wood or fuel for
burning them.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bricklayer</ent>⟦br⟧
